    'direct', 'chatgpt.com', 'twitter', 'linkedin', 
    'youtube', 'bing'
  ) THEN ${mart_conversions_multi_touch.channel_source}
  ELSE 'other' 
END

measures.label: Monthly Self Reported Attribution Source Count

raw_sql_select.sql:
select 
    date_trunc('month' , i.created_at_pt::date) as "Month of Signup"
    , case when i.user_source = '' or i.user_source is null then 'null' else i.user_source end as "User Source"
    , count(*) as "Signup Count"
from training_database.public.dim_identities i
    join TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM a on i.lindy_user_id = a.lindy_user_id
where 
    i.filtered_core = 'true'
    and i.created_at_pt::date between '2024-12-30' and dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('month', current_date()))
        --(date_trunc('week' , current_date)::date - 1)
    and i.created_at_pt::date NOT between '2025-06-16' and '2025-07-06' -- bad data weeks (exclude)
    and "User Source" <> 'null'
group by 1,2
order by 1 asc , 3 desc

select 
    date_trunc('month' , i.created_at_pt::date) as "Month of Signup"
    , case when i.user_source = '' or i.user_source is null then 'null' else i.user_source end as "User Source"
    , count(*) as "Signup Count"
from training_database.public.dim_identities i
    join TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM a on i.lindy_user_id = a.lindy_user_id
where 
    i.filtered_core = 'true'
    and i.created_at_pt::date between '2024-12-30' and dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('month', current_date()))
        --(date_trunc('week' , current_date)::date - 1)
    and i.created_at_pt::date NOT between '2025-06-16' and '2025-07-06' -- bad data weeks (exclude)
    and "User Source" <> 'null'
group by 1,2
order by 1 asc , 3 desc

measures.label: Weekly Self Reported Attribution Source Count

raw_sql_select.sql:
select 
    date_trunc('week', i.created_at_pt::date) as "Week of Signup"
    , case when i.user_source = '' or i.user_source is null then 'null' else i.user_source end as "User Source"
    , count(*) as "Signup Count"
    , round(count(*) * 100.0 / sum(count(*)) over (partition by date_trunc('week', i.created_at_pt::date)) , 1) as "Percent of Weekly Signups"
from training_database.public.dim_identities i
    join TRAINING_DATABASE.PUBLIC.IDENTITIES_ADDENDUM a on i.lindy_user_id = a.lindy_user_id
where 
    i.filtered_core = 'true'
    and i.created_at_pt::date between '2024-12-30' and dateadd('day', -1, date_trunc('week', current_date()))
    and i.created_at_pt::date NOT between '2025-06-16' and '2025-07-06' -- bad data weeks (exclude)
    and "User Source" <> 'null'
group by 1,2
order by 1 asc, 4 desc

raw_sql_select.sql:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('WEEK', "INFERRED_FIRST_ARR_DATE") AS "fct_customer_daily_ts.inferred_first_arr_date[week]", COUNT(DISTINCT "UNIQUE_USER_ID") AS "fct_customer_daily_ts.cohort_size", SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN "CUSTOMER_TYPE" = 'SLG' AND "INFERRED_FIRST_ARR_DATE" = "DAY_START" OR "CUSTOMER_TYPE" = 'PLG' AND "INFERRED_FIRST_ARR_DATE" = "DAY_START" THEN "THIS_DAY_ARR" ELSE NULL END) AS "fct_customer_daily_ts.starting_arr"
FROM "FCT_CUSTOMER_DAILY_TS" AS "fct_customer_daily_ts"
GROUP BY ROLLUP(1)
ORDER BY 3 DESC NULLS LAST
LIMIT 1000
